author: jan
msg: Made the opening of databases asynchronous, so that requests to open databases that are already in the open database cache do not have to wait on the file system.

author: jan
msg: Changed process tree shutdown to be synchronous, to eliminate spurious test failures caused by processes not shutdown fast enough or at the wrong time.
